filter_expression.info:
Optional JSON configuration for search filtering, result limits, and score thresholds.

Format 1 - Explicit filters:
{"filter": [{"term": {"filename":"doc.pdf"}}, {"terms":{"owner":["user1","user2"]}}], "limit": 10, "score_threshold": 1.6}

Format 2 - Context-style mapping:
{"data_sources":["file.pdf"], "document_types":["application/pdf"], "owners":["user123"]}

Use __IMPOSSIBLE_VALUE__ as placeholder to ignore specific filters.
